launch

idl> example

[before: cp param_plot.idl.minimal param_plot.idl]

----

I/O

input: IDL save file example.idl
output: ps and png figure

----

routines

map_latlon.pro: to plot the fields
param_plot.idl: settings for the plot (not compulsory)
example.pro: main routine

colorbar.pro, plot_vector.pro, vector.pro: needed by map_latlon.pro (from Coyote IDL and IDL for meteorology, slightly modified)
fsc/*: to have nice postscript files (from Coyote IDL, slightly modified)(not compulsory, just have to change example.pro and use set_plot)


added:
profile
section
getcdf
reverse_ct
